⚠️  CRITICAL RULE ⚠️

NEVER USE FAKE DATA

✅ DO:
- Real web scraping (YC, Indie Hackers, Product Hunt)
- Real APIs (when available)
- Known real companies as fallback

❌ DON'T:
- Ask AI to "find" or "generate" companies
- Use mock data ("John Doe", "Example.com")
- Ship placeholder data

🧪 BEFORE DEPLOY:
node test/validate-real-data-only.js

📖 READ:
NEVER-USE-FAKE-DATA.md

